{"id":12560,"slug":"eigentumsweiher","url":"https://www.hejfish.com/d/12560-eigentumsweiher","name":"Eigentumsweiher","seo_name":"Eigentumsweiher","description":"<p>Der Eigentumsweiher zwischen Eichenkofen und Eitting konnte im Jahr 1976 erworben werden. Mit seiner Größe von etwa 9 Hektar bietet er genug Möglichkeiten, den Fischen nachzustellen.<br></p> <p>Er ist über die Zufahrt am Kieswerk der Fa. Haslberger zu erreichen. Es können Forellen, Saiblinge, Renken, Karpfen, Hechte, Barsche, Schleien, Brachsen und andere Weißfische gefangen werden.<br></p> <p>Alle gesetzlich erlaubten Köder dürfen verwendet werden.<br></p>","intro":"","details":"","borders":"<p>Ufer!</p>","image":"https://file.hejfish.com/image/cc1200x900/03/b7/03b732101cde0532316e5bb6818a1bdc5d50cc36.jpeg","water_size_ha":null,"fish":["Karpfen","Hecht","Renke","Flussbarsch","Div. Weißfische","Regenbogenforelle","Schuppenkarpfen"],"techniques":["Ansitzangeln","Fliegenfischen","Hegenenangeln","Naturköderangeln","Spinnangeln","Posenangeln","Raubfischangeln","Friedfischangeln"],"properties":[],"water_type":"Teich (Weiher)","rules_text":"","rules_files":[],"tickets":[],"ticket_types":[],"manager":{"id":1604,"name":"Bezirksfischereiverein Erding e.V. ","street":"In den Hacken 3","postal_code":"85435","city":"Erding","telephone":"+49 8122  8474948","email":"kassier@fischen-erding.de","website":"https://www.fischen-erding.de","logo":"https://file.hejfish.com/image/r200x200/44/f5/44f5abcab4c4aba5673f50821fb6209fbbaccd8b.png","slug":"bezirksfischereiverein-erding-e-v"},"season_begin":"0001-01-01","season_end":"0001-12-31","features":{"accessible":false,"public_transport":false,"boat":false,"belly_boat":false,"digital_ticket":false,"night_fishing":false,"ice_fishing":false,"depth_map":true,"has_gauges":true},"location":{"city":{"id":32456,"name":"Erding"},"district":{"id":414,"name":"Kreis Erding"},"state":{"id":10,"name":"Bayern","slug":"bayern"},"country":{"id":2,"name":"Deutschland","code":"de","slug":"deutsch